Platform Pro Boxes Widget
by Scott Meves, 2010
http://stereointeractive.com/blog

This wordpress widget allows you to specify a box set to display in your sidebar. Works with Pagelines Platform Pro theme.

Add it to your theme by copying the widget source code to your theme's folder and including it in your functions.php:

<?php
// in functions.php
require_once(dirname(__FILE__).'/widget.boxes.php');